{"ja348:0.1":"Jataka ","ja348:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja348:0.3":"Culakunalavagga ","ja348:0.4":"8. Arannajataka ","ja348:1.1":"“Aranna gamamagamma, ","ja348:1.2":"kimsilam kimvatam aham; ","ja348:1.3":"Purisam tata seveyyam, ","ja348:1.4":"tam me akkhahi pucchito”. ","ja348:2.1":"“Yo tam vissasaye tata, ","ja348:2.2":"vissasanca khameyya te; ","ja348:2.3":"Sussusi ca titikkhi ca, ","ja348:2.4":"tam bhajehi ito gato. ","ja348:3.1":"Yassa kayena vacaya, ","ja348:3.2":"manasa natthi dukkatam; ","ja348:3.3":"Urasiva patitthaya, ","ja348:3.4":"tam bhajehi ito gato. ","ja348:4.1":"Haliddiragam kapicittam, ","ja348:4.2":"purisam ragaviraginam; ","ja348:4.3":"Tadisam tata ma sevi, ","ja348:4.4":"nimmanussampi ce siya”ti. ","ja348:5.1":"Arannajatakam atthamam. "}